== Code ==
<pre>{{Infobox Dungeon
|name    =
|image   =
|caption =
|tokens  =
|location =
}}</pre>

== Usage ==
To use this template, place the code above at the top of an article and fill in the respective blanks.

'''Where:'''
*<code>name</code> should be filled with the name of the dungeon.
*<code>image</code> should be filled with the background image of the dungeon (from the screen before you start the dungeon).
*<code>caption</code> should be filled with a description of the <code>image</code> spot.
*<code>tokens</code> should be filled with the number of dungeon tokens needed to enter the dungeon.
*<code>location</code> should be filled with the general location of the dungeon; i.e., Viridian Forest is north of Viridian City on Route 2.
